            <div class="col span_4_of_5 contextual-region article-col">
              <h1 itemprop="name" class="article-title">Malta’s crypto assets plan means greater AML risks, IMF warns</h1>
              
              <h2 class="article-sub-title">Authorities must rapidly improve AML regime and guarantee FSA’s independence, mission says</h2>            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>
<div class="content">
  <main role="main" class="content-inner">
    <div class="main-content">
      <article class="section group article-content">
        <div class="col span_1_of_5"></div>
        <div class="col span_4_of_5 article-col">
                                    <figure class="main landscape-large">
        <img src="/sites/risk/files/styles/landscape_750_463/public/import/IMG/269/249269/malta-introduction-580x358.jpg?itok=GYLza1hK" width="750" height="463" alt="Malta" title="Malta" typeof="foaf:Image" />



<figcaption>
        <div class="caption-text">Malta’s government has tried to make the island a centre for firms using blockchain and similar technology</div>
      </figcaption>

</figure>                                <div class="article-meta-container group">
                        <ul class="meta-taxonomy-list author-dateline">
              
      
